(Business Flow) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (This document describes the end-to-end business flow for the Maritime Operations &) Tj
T* (  Compliance System. It is intended for reviewers and can be exported to PDF for submission.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  User Access Flow) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  An admin logs in using email or username and password.) Tj
T* (  The backend validates credentials and verifies that the account is active.) Tj
T* (  The backend issues access and refresh JWT cookies plus a CSRF cookie.) Tj
T* (  If the user must reset a temporary password, they are redirected to the reset-password) Tj
T* (  flow.) Tj
T* (  The user is routed to the correct workspace:) Tj
T* (   - Admin users use dashboard, maintenance, drill, attendance, users, security, and) Tj
T* (  profile pages.) Tj
T* (   - Crew users use dashboard, crew workspace, security, and profile pages.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  User Management Flow) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  An admin opens the Users page.) Tj
T* (  User cards show account details, role, ship assignment, activity status, last login,) Tj
T* (  assigned drill count, and completed drill count.) Tj
T* (  Admins can create users from the Add User modal.) Tj
T* (  Admins can edit user details from the Edit action on the user card.) Tj
T* (  Admins can reset a user's password. This revokes active sessions and requires a password) Tj
T* (  change on next login.) Tj
T* (  Admins can deactivate a user. Deactivated users cannot log in and active sessions are) Tj
T* (  revoked.) Tj
T* (  The backend prevents duplicate email/username accounts and prevents deactivating or) Tj
T* (  demoting the final active admin.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  Ship and Access Flow) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  Super Admins can view all ships.) Tj
T* (  Ship-scoped admins and crew members see only their assigned ship.) Tj
T* (  API filters enforce ship access server-side.) Tj
T* (  Frontend dropdowns only display ships returned by the backend.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  Maintenance Flow) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  Admin creates a maintenance task for a ship.) Tj
T* (  Admin assigns the task to one crew member, multiple crew members, or all eligible crew on) Tj
T* (  that ship.) Tj
T* (  Crew members see only tasks assigned to them.) Tj
T* (  Crew can update task status.) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
