(  Completed tasks record completion timestamp and completing user.) Tj
T* (  Dashboard metrics treat open tasks past due date as overdue.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  Safety Drill Flow) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  Admin schedules a drill with drill type, ship, date, start time, and end time.) Tj
T* (  The backend validates that end time is after start time.) Tj
T* (  Eligible crew for the ship are snapshotted into attendance rows.) Tj
T* (  A drill is scheduled before start time.) Tj
T* (  A drill becomes active between start time and end time.) Tj
T* (  Crew can mark attendance or completion only while active.) Tj
T* (  After end time, drill records become read-only.) Tj
T* (  New crew added after a drill is completed do not appear in that historical drill) Tj
T* (  attendance list.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  Attendance Reporting Flow) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  Admin opens the Attendance page.) Tj
T* (  The system loads drill attendance rows across selected drills.) Tj
T* (  Filters can be applied by ship, drill type, date range, crew member, and attendance) Tj
T* (  status.) Tj
T* (  If filters return no matching data, the page shows a clear "No records found" state.) Tj
T* (  Large reports use load-more pagination on the frontend.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  Compliance Dashboard Flow) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  Dashboard requests compliance metrics from the backend.) Tj
T* (  Backend refreshes drill statuses based on server time.) Tj
T* (  Backend applies role and ship scoping.) Tj
T* (  Backend calculates:) Tj
T* (   - total ships visible to the user) Tj
T* (   - maintenance total/completed/overdue) Tj
T* (   - drill total/completed/missed) Tj
T* (   - maintenance compliance percentage) Tj
T* (   - drill participation percentage) Tj
T* (  Frontend displays metrics, risk lists, and visual progress indicators.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  Profile Flow) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  Any authenticated user can open Profile.) Tj
T* (  Users can update their display name.) Tj
T* (  Users can change password after entering the old password.) Tj
T* (  Users cannot change their own role, ship assignment, or restricted account settings.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (  Security Flow) Tj
ET
endstream
endobj
